Title Review: I think that for the application to work in short  you must activate the feature to monitor your site through Google Map. You must register with this application using the personal number. This application is government and the Ministry of Health monitors all patients with this epidemic  whether a patient is quarantined or was in the 14-day home quarantine period .. And all These are monitored by the personal number and the address of the residence ..
